---
title: "Ep 398: Dissecting Ultimate Spider-Man"
publishDate: "2025-09-05"
category: "major-issues"
episodeNumber: 398
spotifyUrl: "https://comicbookclique.podbean.com/e/ep-398-dissecting-ultimate-spider-man/"
